rning signs.<ref name=\"auto1\" />\n\nA consortium of Chinese medical experts charged by the Chinese CDC with investigating the inception of the virus published their report in ''[[The Lancet]]'', reporting details of 41 first known patients.<ref name=Wang24Jan2020>{{Cite journal|url=https://www.thelancet.com/journals/lancet/article/PIIS0140-6736(20)30185-9/abstract|title=A novel coronavirus outbreak of global health concern|first1=Chen|last1=Wang|first2=Peter W.|last2=Horby|first3=Frederick G.|last3=Hayden|first4=George F.|last4=Gao|date=24 January 2020|journal=The Lancet|volume=0|issue=10223|pages=470\u2013473|via=www.thelancet.com|doi=10.1016/S0140-6736(20)30185-9|pmid=31986257}}</ref>\n\nBy the end of the day, the entire Hubei province had gone under a city-by-city quarantine, apart from [[Xiangyang]] and [[Shennongjia|Shennongjia Forestry District]].\n\n===25 January===\n[[Communist Party of China|Chinese Communist Party]] [[General Secretary of the Communist Party of China|general secretary]] [[Xi Jinping]] called the \"accelerating spread\" of the coronavirus a \"grave situation\" in a [[Politburo of the Communist Party of China|Party Politburo]] meeting,<ref name=\"People's Daily Online\">{{cite news|url=http://en.people.cn/n3/2020/0125/c90000-9651799.html|title=CPC leadership meets to discuss novel coronavirus prevention, control|date=25 January 2020|work=People's Daily Online|quote=Xi Jinping, general secretary of the CPC Central Committee, chaired the meeting.|access-date=8 February 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200125202946/http://en.people.cn/n3/2020/0125/c90000-9651799.html|archive-date=25 January 2020|url-status=live}}</ref> and that it was \"mutating\" as Beijing escalates measures to contain the illness.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/asia/coronavirus-news-china-new-year-latest-wuhan-symptoms-virus-uk-france-australia-jinping-a9302011.html|title=Spread of coronavirus 'accelerating', warns China presiden