/wuhan-virus-malaysia-confirms-first-3-cases-all-patients-related-12331172|title=Wuhan virus: Malaysia confirms first 3 cases; all patients related to Chinese national who was Singapore's first case|website=CNA|access-date=2020-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200125065344/https://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/asia/wuhan-virus-malaysia-confirms-first-3-cases-all-patients-related-12331172|archive-date=2020-01-25|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name=\"Malaysia25Jan\">{{cite news|url=https://www.nst.com.my/news/nation/2020/01/559563/breaking-3-coronavirus-cases-confirmed-johor-baru|title=[Breaking] 3 coronavirus cases confirmed in Johor Baru|last1=Times|first1=New Straits|date=25 January 2020|work=NST Online|accessdate=25 January 2020}}</ref> and a fourth case later.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.straitstimes.com/asia/se-asia/malaysia-confirms-first-cases-of-wuhan-coronavirus-infection|title=Wuhan virus: Malaysia confirms 4 cases, 3 patients related to Singapore's first confirmed case|last=hermesauto|date=2020-01-25|website=The Straits Times|access-date=2020-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200125235636/https://www.straitstimes.com/asia/se-asia/malaysia-confirms-first-cases-of-wuhan-coronavirus-infection|archive-date=2020-01-25|url-status=live}}</ref> Japan confirmed its third case.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-china-health-japan-idUSKBN1ZO08O|title=Japan confirms third case of Wuhan virus|date=2020-01-25|work=Reuters|access-date=2020-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200125094237/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-china-health-japan-idUSKBN1ZO08O|archive-date=2020-01-25|url-status=live}}</ref> Canada confirmed its first case in [[Toronto]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://sunnybrook.ca/media/item.asp?c=1&i=2043&f=novel-coronavirus-2020|title=Patient admitted with novel coronavirus - Sunnybrook Hospital|website=sunnybrook.ca|access-date=2020-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200126001007/https:/