es of coronavirus as illness spreads to 20 countries|first=Doug|last=Stanglin|website=USA TODAY|access-date=2020-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200206103724/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/world/2020/01/31/coronavirus-symptoms-britain-russia-who-wuhan-emergency/4620574002/|archive-date=2020-02-06|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/health-51325192|title=Coronavirus: Two cases confirmed in UK|accessdate=31 January 2020|website=BBC|date=31 January 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200131100345/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/health-51325192|archive-date=31 January 2020|url-status=live}}</ref> The first Swedish and Spanish cases were confirmed.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.aftonbladet.se/a/GGgL49|title=F\u00f6rsta bekr\u00e4ftade fallet av coronavirus i Sverige \u2013 kvinna h\u00e5lls isolerad|website=Aftonbladet|access-date=2020-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200201052456/https://www.aftonbladet.se/a/GGgL49|archive-date=2020-02-01|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.yahoo.com/news/spain-confirms-first-case-coronavirus-222027208.html|title=Spain Confirms First Case of Coronavirus|website=Yahoo|access-date=2020-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200131232132/https://www.yahoo.com/news/spain-confirms-first-case-coronavirus-222027208.html|archive-date=2020-01-31|url-status=live}}</ref> The seventh confirmed case in the U.S. is in [[Santa Clara County, California]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://abc7news.com/5895060/|title=LIVE: Coronavirus: Bay Area's 1st case confirmed in Santa Clara County, CDC says|date=2020-01-31|website=ABC7 San Francisco|language=en|access-date=2020-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200131215242/https://abc7news.com/5895060/|archive-date=2020-01-31|url-status=live}}</ref> A fourth case of coronavirus in Canada has been confirmed in [[London, Ontario|London]], Ontario.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://nationalpost.com/news/world/cor