152.html|archive-date=2020-01-25|url-status=live}}</ref> Shandong,<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.jiemian.com/article/3910357.html|title=\u5c71\u4e1c\u7701\u542f\u52a8\u91cd\u5927\u7a81\u53d1\u516c\u5171\u536b\u751f\u4e8b\u4ef6\u4e00\u7ea7\u54cd\u5e94{{!}}\u754c\u9762\u65b0\u95fb \u00b7 \u5feb\u8baf|website=www.jiemian.com|access-date=2020-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200125072915/https://www.jiemian.com/article/3910357.html|archive-date=2020-01-25|url-status=live}}</ref> Fujian,<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.jiemian.com/article/3910558.html|title=\u798f\u5efa\u7701\u542f\u52a8\u91cd\u5927\u7a81\u53d1\u516c\u5171\u536b\u751f\u4e8b\u4ef6\u4e00\u7ea7\u54cd\u5e94{{!}}\u754c\u9762\u65b0\u95fb \u00b7 \u5feb\u8baf|website=www.jiemian.com|access-date=2020-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200125072913/https://www.jiemian.com/article/3910558.html|archive-date=2020-01-25|url-status=live}}</ref> Guangxi,<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.jiemian.com/article/3910597.html|title=\u5e7f\u897f\u542f\u52a8\u91cd\u5927\u7a81\u53d1\u516c\u5171\u536b\u751f\u4e8b\u4ef6\u4e00\u7ea7\u54cd\u5e94{{!}}\u754c\u9762\u65b0\u95fb \u00b7 \u5feb\u8baf|website=www.jiemian.com|access-date=2020-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200125072917/https://www.jiemian.com/article/3910597.html|archive-date=2020-01-25|url-status=live}}</ref> and Hebei<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.jiemian.com/article/3910664.html|title=\u6cb3\u5317\u7701\u542f\u52a8\u91cd\u5927\u7a81\u53d1\u516c\u5171\u536b\u751f\u4e8b\u4ef6\u4e00\u7ea7\u54cd\u5e94{{!}}\u754c\u9762\u65b0\u95fb \u00b7 \u5feb\u8baf|website=www.jiemian.com|access-date=2020-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200125160947/https://www.jiemian.com/article/3910664.html|archive-date=2020-01-25|url-status=live}}</ref> declared a level 1 public health emergency, in chronological order.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cgtn.com/special/Battling-the-novel-coronavirus-What-we-know-so-far-.html|title=Latest on the cor